$ R: DBI::dbConnect - encoding

The following simple → development/languages/R[R] script is supposed to check the influence of the `encoding` parameter on a → development/databases[database] connection.

It is currently able to connect to an → development/databases/SQLite[SQLite] database with the → development/languages/R/packages/RSQLite[`RSQLite` package] or to
→ development/databases/SQL-Server[SQL Server] via the → development/languages/R/packages/odbc[`odbc` package].

gh|about-R|/packages/DBI/dbConnect/encoding.R||

sa:

  → development/Unicode/character-encoding

  The → development/languages/R/packages/DBI[`DBI` package]
